lyrics:
(Verse 1)
In the glow of screens, in the silence of dreams,
We're drifting, it seems, through digital streams.
Voices whisper low, in a world that doesn't know,
The weight of the shadow, in the neon glow.

(Chorus)
Floating, falling, through the ether calling,
In the echo of the void, where the stars are stalling.
Disconnected hearts, in a world apart,
Searching for a start, in the art of the dark.
